description: Locals in the north-east can now travel after the court said the ban was "disproportionate".
title: Coronavirus: German region eases Baltic coast travel ban
title_page: Coronavirus: German region eases Baltic coast travel ban - BBC News
maintext: And the death toll has reached 2,373, with another 266 fatalities reported on Friday - still well below the death rates in Italy, Spain, France and the UK. Johns Hopkins University in the US puts the number of infections in Germany at over 118,000 with more than 2,600 deaths.
